{"tid":1447940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Ghost Buster]捉鬼方法集思廣益","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:49.000Z","uid":35639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1f9c86943fbf2239535443a87acf9c87be0d63","tid":1447940,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"農曆7月周街遊魂野鬼<br />\n點先分到佢係人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n1. 望聞問切<br />\n係d鬼未張牙舞爪前<br />\n就要留意下佢地有無咩特別之處<br />\n相傳有d鬼好中意戴住耳機聽跑馬仔<br />\n就咁睇分唔清?<br />\n搵人周圍行 <span style=\"color: red;\">逐個問 一對一</span>：你係咪人呀？你係咪鬼呀？ 又或者俾個對聯佢對一對 &ldquo;香港驚賊&ldquo;<br />\n如果佢支吾以對 或者唔識駁<br />\n大家要即刻大叫有鬼呀<br />\n如果佢神色慌張或者有咩特別行為 就係捉鬼好時機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.一人一道符<br />\n鬼好驚符 如果道符寫住d野關佢地事就仲驚<br />\n道符既內容可以同第一點個對聯相近<br />\n而且要放係當眼地方<br />\n大家見到其他「人」未有符<br />\n不防可以送一道俾佢提佢放係身防鬼<br />\n如果佢唔肯放 佢係鬼既可能性就高好多<br />\n不過符製作需時<br />\n後勤道士要幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他捉鬼大法？"},{"pid":"603d900b19119e5186af380ba30315801eda8476","tid":1447940,"uid":35639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"屌開錯台"},{"pid":"3827b0de318116e7782f4bfbc3c198ab50ed6311","tid":1447940,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/41nSRUAKcUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F41nSRUAKcUL.jpg&h=e6ca347f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e292b4c958bb25a849978422d20b62655cfe645e","tid":1447940,"uid":136457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsPaqZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsPaqZu.jpg&h=92865fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港已經唔容許普通市民存在"}]}